SYNOPSIS

    In your weaver.ini:

     [-App::lcpan]

DESCRIPTION

    This plugin is to be used when building App::lcpan::* distribution.
    Currently it does the following:

    For each lib/App/lcpan/CmdBundle/* module files:

      * Add general Description text

    For each lib/App/lcpan/Cmd/* module files:

      * Add general Description text

